text.p: These are the leading stories in the Tunisian press on Wednesday. Reuters has not verified these stories and does not vouch for their accuracy.
- President Ben Ali on Tuesday held a meeting with Egyptian President Hosni Mubarak. They discussed the Middle East peace process and bilateral cooperation.
- Prime Minister Hamed Karoui to represent Tunisia at the Francophone summit in Burkina Faso.
- Ben Ali and Mubarak talks stresed the need to boost cooperation and trade exchanges between Tunisia and Egypt.
